OL,3,CEveryday's a 'battle' for sales, says
OL,4,C142-year-old firm betting on TikTok
OL,5,CShop
OL,7,FThe maker of Imperial Leather and
OL,8,FSanctuary Spa has said reaching
OL,9,Fshoppers on platforms like TikTok Shop
OL,10,Fwas as important as Tesco, as the 142-
OL,11,Fyear-old business vies to compete with
OL,12,Fa rising cohort of social media-savvy
OL,13,Fbrands.
OL,15,FPZ Cussons ` the consumer goods giant
OL,16,Fthat was founded in 1884 and is behind
OL,17,Fa swathe of beauty, hygiene and baby
OL,18,Fproducts ` said it had been investing
OL,19,Fmore into innovation and building its
OL,20,Fbrands.
