OL,3,CEveryday's a 'battle' for sales, says
OL,4,C142-year-old firm betting on TikTok
OL,5,CShop
OL,7,FChief executive Jonathan Myers said
OL,8,Fthe business has to "battle every day
OL,9,Fto win every purchase".
OL,11,F"There's hardly a store in the country
OL,12,Fthat sells a washing and bathing
OL,13,Fproduct that doesn't sell a PZ Cussons
OL,14,Fproduct," he told the Press
OL,15,FAssociation.
OL,17,FBut he said the company had been
OL,18,Ftrying to be at the forefront of
OL,19,Fonline shopping trends that many newer
OL,20,Fbrands are tapping into.
