OL,3,CEveryday's a 'battle' for sales, says
OL,4,C142-year-old firm betting on TikTok
OL,5,CShop
OL,7,F"If you look at the way that most of
OL,8,Fthe insurgent brands are arriving,
OL,9,Fit's through social media, and that
OL,10,Fblurs into e-commerce platforms, for
OL,11,Fexample TikTok Shop," he said.
OL,13,F"It's about making sure that we're
OL,14,Fpresent, that we're growing fast, and
OL,15,Fthat we're stealing our share of
OL,16,Fpurchases there, just as we would a
OL,17,FTesco Express down the street."
