OL,7,FTikTok Shop, the e-commerce arm of the
OL,8,Fvideo-sharing social media platform
OL,9,Fwhere users can buy and sell products,
OL,10,Fhas grown rapidly over recent years.
OL,12,FMajor retailers like Marks & Spencer
OL,13,Fand Sainsbury's are now selling
OL,14,Fproducts on the marketplace alongside
OL,15,Fthousands of smaller businesses and
OL,16,Fbrands.
