OL,3,CEveryday's a 'battle' for sales, says
OL,4,C142-year-old firm betting on TikTok
OL,5,CShop
OL,7,FTikTok Shop recently said it had
OL,8,Fbecome the fourth-largest beauty
OL,9,Fretailer in the UK, according to data
OL,10,Ffrom NielsenIQ, while beauty sales on
OL,11,Fthe platform soared by 60% year-on-
OL,12,Fyear in 2025 fuelled by trends such as
OL,13,FKorean skincare.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, PZ Cussons' Mr Myers
OL,16,Fhighlighted the business's activity in
OL,17,FIndonesia ` where it has been
OL,18,Fexperimenting with new sales tactics,
OL,19,Fincluding a live-streaming channel
OL,20,Ffrom its factory.
