OL,4,C142-year-old firm betting on TikTok
OL,5,CShop
OL,7,FHe said: "We run three shifts of live-
OL,8,Fstreamers who are driving demand for
OL,9,Four brands that is then fulfilled
OL,10,Fthrough marketplaces like TikTok Shop,
OL,11,Fand delivered on the back of a moped."
OL,13,FTikTok sales in Indonesia have
OL,14,Fincreased more than 600%, where PZ
OL,15,FCussons currently operates a TikTok
OL,16,FShop.
