OL,7,FThe chief executive said he could
OL,8,F"definitely see the rise of quick
OL,9,Fcommerce" in urban areas of the UK,
OL,10,Faccelerated by the "blurring" of
OL,11,Fsocial media and shopping channels.
OL,13,FMr Myers stressed that there was no
OL,14,Froom for "complacency", adding:
OL,15,F"Competition is good because it keeps
OL,16,Fus on our toes."
